move inside my head.

02:36.406 --> 02:37.615
It's called abulia.

02:37.741 --> 02:40.868
The inability to
make a decision or exercise will.

02:40.994 --> 02:42.203
Is it going to happen again?

02:42.329 --> 02:44.956
It's part of a TIA.
A transient ischemic attack.

02:45.082 --> 02:47.124
Blood was cut off to a section
of your frontal lobe.

02:47.251 --> 02:48.876
Is it like a stroke
or something?

02:49.002 --> 02:49.919
