Before that, I walked dogs.

03:30.586 --> 03:33.129
And before that...

03:34.464 --> 03:37.425
Loss of free will. I like it.

03:38.218 --> 03:41.012
Maybe we can get
Thomas Aquinas in for a consult.

03:41.805 --> 03:43.139
What caused the TIA?

03:43.473 --> 03:45.099
