No sign of a clot.

03:45.392 --> 03:47.435
Could have dissolved.
Most likely came from her heart.

03:47.561 --> 03:48.436
We should do a bubble study.

03:48.770 --> 03:51.022
Clots are unlikely
in a 28-year-old who's not on the pill.

03:51.356 --> 03:53.232
