caused by drugs.

03:53.358 --> 03:55.943
I don't think so.
She goes from job to job.

03:56.069 --> 03:57.945
Maybe there's some kind
of ADD here.

03:58.280 --> 03:59.614
Help us pinpoint
where the neurological...

03:59.740 --> 04:02.408
She goes from job to job
because she's a scam artist.

04:02.534 --> 04:04.827
