to qualify for unemployment,

04:04.953 --> 04:06.454
then gets fired
and gets high.

04:06.663 --> 04:08.539
I still don't think
it's drugs.

04:08.665 --> 04:09.999
Did you check
for infection?

04:10.125 --> 04:11.417
LP showed nothing.
No fever.

04:11.543 --> 04:12.543
White blood count is normal.

04:12.669 --> 04:13.628
Could be toxic exposure.

04:13.921 --> 04:15.796
You're the one always saying
it must be drugs.

04:15.923 --> 04:18.132
You figure she's a minority,
she must be stoned?

04:18.258 --> 04:20.176
- You know that's not what I...
- She seems like a nice girl.

04:20.302 --> 04:21.427
You haven't met her!

04:21.553 --> 04:23.429
She was pregnant at 15,
dropped out of high school.

04:23.555 --> 04:24.889
She's a real overachiever.

04:25.015 --> 04:27.099
Come on. Cut her some slack.
Her baby died of SIDS.

04:27.225 --> 04:28.351
This isn't some
romantic story

04:28.477 --> 04:30.102
about a nice girl
scarred by tragedy.

04:30.228 --> 04:32.563
She's a drug-using scam artist
scarred by tragedy.

04:32.689 --> 04:35.232
On the other hand,
the tox screen just came back.

04:35.359 --> 04:36.525
She's clean.

04:36.652 --> 04:38.694
You're wasting my time.
He's wasting...

04:43.533 --> 04:45.952
Second ex-Mrs. Wilson
want money?

04:47.079 --> 04:48.496
I am no longer
paying alimony.

04:48.622 --> 04:50.122
She wanted
her independence,

04:50.248 --> 04:51.499
so she got her
realtor's license.

