- She wants me to take Hector.

05:00.175 --> 05:01.342
Pool boy?

05:01.969 --> 05:03.052
Dog.

05:03.178 --> 05:04.095
No longer interested.

05:04.304 --> 05:06.347
We got him
on our honeymoon.

05:06.473 --> 05:08.516
So I'm like
the other parent.

05:08.642 --> 05:09.934
