Besides, I'm always here.

05:13.271 --> 05:14.605
I asked Cuddy
to a play Thursday.

05:18.944 --> 05:20.486
Oh, you... Okay.

05:20.988 --> 05:22.363
She said she was busy.

05:22.489 --> 05:26.075
And you didn't believe her,
so you bribed a janitor,

05:26.201 --> 05:28.536
broke into her computer,
checked her appointments...

05:28.662 --> 05:30.413
I asked her as a test.

05:30.539 --> 05:32.540
What would you have learned
if she'd said yes?

05:32.666 --> 05:33.958
A lot about bondage.

05:34.626 --> 05:36.002
She was busy for me
but not for you.

05:36.128 --> 05:38.212
She's not interested
in play qua play.

05:38.338 --> 05:39.922
She's interested in you.

05:40.048 --> 05:43.759
No. I'm not getting sucked into the
vortex of your insanity again.

05:43.885 --> 05:44.927
Don't pass me
notes in class.

05:45.053 --> 05:46.429
Don't tell me to
ask her to the prom.

05:46.555 --> 05:47.972
