It's nice to see her relax.

06:05.949 --> 06:09.243
So all this enjoying
is an act of charity.

06:09.453 --> 06:11.746
I'm keeping the receipts
for tax purposes.

06:17.252 --> 06:20.755
What's life without the ability
to make stupid choices?

06:21.173 --> 06:22.506
She needs her free will.

06:22.632 --> 06:25.718
