I'll get the office to myself.

06:30.599 --> 06:33.059
There's a lot of porn
piling up on the Internet.

06:33.185 --> 06:34.393
Doesn't download itself.

06:38.065 --> 06:39.440
Eric? Eric!

06:39.983 --> 06:40.816
Hello, Mr. Foreman.

06:42.194 --> 06:44.653
- Dr. Chase. How are you?
- Good.

06:44.780 --> 06:46.072
You're lucky
you caught us, actually...

06:46.198 --> 06:47.281
I'll meet you outside.

06:49.367 --> 06:53.913
Hey, Dad. I've got to go.
Why are you here?

06:54.039 --> 06:55.873
Everything okay?

06:55.999 --> 06:56.916
