about it on the phone.

07:06.051 --> 07:07.927
You said you couldn't
come home.

07:08.762 --> 07:09.595
You didn't have to come.

07:09.930 --> 07:13.182
You haven't been home
in eight years.

07:14.851 --> 07:16.602
She should see you,

07:17.354 --> 07:18.979
while she still
knows who you are.

07:21.942 --> 07:25.111
Dad. I've talked to her
on the phone.

07:25.904 --> 07:29.490
She only knows
who I am sometimes.

07:29.908 --> 07:31.617
Sometimes

07:33.120 --> 07:34.662
is important.

07:37.040 --> 07:40.042
So what's up with your dad?
Didn't know he was gonna be in town?

07:40.168 --> 07:41.001
No.

07:43.255 --> 07:46.132
Building this old, could be
toxic exposure anywhere.

07:46.258 --> 07:49.677
Asbestos, mold, the coloring agents
in the old wallpaper.

07:49.803 --> 07:51.720
Or it could be drugs.

07:52.222 --> 07:53.764
I thought we ruled out...

07:55.475 --> 07:58.144
Clean tox screen means
drugs didn't cause the TIA.

07:58.353 --> 08:00.187
Drugs can be laced
with toxic substances.

08:00.313 --> 08:02.064
Arsenic, rat poison.

08:02.190 --> 08:03.399
The drugs wash out
of her system,

08:03.525 --> 08:04.358
the toxins stick around.

08:04.568 --> 08:06.360
Exposure could come about
any number of ways.

08:06.486 --> 08:08.320
There's no reason to assume
it was through drug use.

08:08.780 --> 08:11.031
Absolutely.
Except for the crack pipe.

08:11.449 --> 08:13.534
I'll test her blood
for arsenic and rat poison.

08:13.660 --> 08:15.744
Yeah. Yeah.
You'd like that, wouldn't you?

08:17.122 --> 08:19.081
And your dad asked you out
for dinner?

08:20.876 --> 08:23.752
I'll do the tests.
You're stuck with your family.

08:27.674 --> 08:29.425
You like Hockney?

08:29.551 --> 08:30.759
You heard about that.

08:32.012 --> 08:34.096
The pop stuff or
the Venezuelan pictures?

08:35.223 --> 08:36.849
That's a trick question.

08:37.601 --> 08:40.811
Yes. But you have no idea
how it's a trick.

08:40.937 --> 08:43.772
I like art. I'm open to new things.
What's the problem?

08:44.024 --> 08:47.359
You're going to a gallery to see
Venezuelan pictures that don't exist.

08:47.485 --> 08:49.195
But you won't go
to a play with me. Why?

08:49.321 --> 08:52.489
House, why is my social life
suddenly red hot?

08:52.616 --> 08:55.159
One minute I'm mushing along
with the huskies as usual

08:55.285 --> 08:57.411
and suddenly
it's global warming.

08:57.537 --> 08:59.914
You think you saw somebody else pick up
a toy from the sandbox

09:00.040 --> 09:01.707
and suddenly you want it.

09:02.584 --> 09:03.584
Is that why you said no?

09:03.919 --> 09:07.713
Maybe I just want a friend
and I thought Wilson was a safe choice.

09:08.632 --> 09:11.300
I'm not safe? Cool.

09:13.511 --> 09:15.846
James Wilson is never
the safe choice.

09:15.972 --> 09:18.307
We're going to a gallery.
We're not getting married.

09:18.433 --> 09:20.017
Sure, you say that now.

09:20.143 --> 09:21.810
He always marries them
in the end.

09:34.783 --> 09:36.867
Is that Eric? Eric!

09:36.993 --> 09:38.035
Oh!

09:39.120 --> 09:41.664
Oh, baby. Baby!

09:43.124 --> 09:46.377
I wanted to find that picture I took
at your high school graduation.

09:46.544 --> 09:47.753
I had it reframed.

09:47.879 --> 09:50.464
It's in one of these
suitcases, but I don't know...

09:50.590 --> 09:51.924
You can show it to me later.

09:59.140 --> 10:01.100
Your father wants to know
if you've been praying.

10:01.518 --> 10:04.061
You don't have to just
come out with it like that.

10:04.479 --> 10:06.855
But I only want to know
if you're happy.

10:06.982 --> 10:08.190
Sure. I'm okay.

10:08.316 --> 10:09.733
You like it here?
You have friends?

10:09.985 --> 10:11.902
Yeah.
Everything is great, Mom.

10:12.028 --> 10:13.779
That's why I brought
the picture for you.

10:14.072 --> 10:15.781
I remember
when you were little

10:15.907 --> 10:18.993
you liked to look in the back of
the math book because you knew

10:19.119 --> 10:20.953
even though it made
no sense then,

10:21.079 --> 10:23.998
by the end of the year
you'd understand it all.

10:24.624 --> 10:26.667
That's why
you brought the picture?

10:26.793 --> 10:30.504
You wanted to look ahead,
to see how far you'd go.

10:30.630 --> 10:33.924
Now you're a grown man,
I thought you might like to look back

10:34.050 --> 10:36.093
to see how far you've come.

10:37.053 --> 10:38.887
It all makes sense now.
Doesn't it?

10:45.603 --> 10:46.770
That isn't mine.

10:46.896 --> 10:48.314
It was in your closet.

10:49.149 --> 10:51.358
It belongs to this guy
who used to live with me.

10:52.068 --> 10:54.820
You might want to let him know
he's got arsenic poisoning.

10:55.864 --> 10:57.197
We should get
a sample of his hair

10:57.324 --> 10:58.657
so we can see
the extent of it.

10:58.783 --> 11:01.493
But I don't do...
I don't do drugs.

11:12.547 --> 11:15.716
Get a crash cart in here!
Respiratory arrest!

11:20.305 --> 11:22.931
Are you sure
it isn't from the arsenic?

11:23.058 --> 11:25.267
