your lungs like this.

11:29.064 --> 11:30.773
We need you
to stay still now.

11:33.109 --> 11:35.194
Six-millimeter cuts
starting at the apices.

11:36.821 --> 11:38.572
Also, I just wanted
to let you know

11:38.698 --> 11:41.158
should you change your mind,
I'll be available.

11:42.494 --> 11:45.037
