of hearing me say it?

11:45.330 --> 11:47.206
I have no intention
of going out with you,

11:47.332 --> 11:49.875
of having sex with you,
of doing anything with you.

11:50.001 --> 11:50.834
Except work.

11:51.127 --> 11:52.628
We don't have to make
a big deal about it.

11:52.754 --> 11:54.213
I just thought
I'd let you know.

11:55.006 --> 11:57.466
I decided Tuesdays would be
a good day to do that.

11:58.468 --> 12:00.594
