the lung bases.

12:13.733 --> 12:14.608
We need to put this
behind us.

12:14.901 --> 12:15.901
Understood.

12:16.027 --> 12:18.987
- But you keep bringing it up.
- You're the one who's still talking.

12:19.489 --> 12:21.907
Look, I'm not demanding
anything from you.

12:22.033 --> 12:25.285
I'm not following you home.
I've got no expectations.

12:25.412 --> 12:28.747
A gentle, polite reminder
once a week is hardly stalking.

12:34.254 --> 12:36.880
There's a mass.
Just outside the lingula.

12:40.844 --> 12:42.177
Biopsy shows
there are white blood cells

12:42.303 --> 12:43.637
